        "text_Xeg7b9": {
          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "subheading": "Your Vision, Our Expertise. ",
            "title": "Make Flowers You’ll Love With Guidance You Can Trust.",
            "heading_font_size": "heading-x-large",
            "text": "<p>Wedding flowers shouldn’t be confusing or expensive — and you shouldn’t have to figure it all out by yourself.  We give you a custom DIY floral plan, easy-to-follow flower recipes, and the exact number of flowers you need to bring your arrangements to life. No guesswork. No wasted money. Just clear guidance and gorgeous results. </p><p>DIY with confidence, with support from real floral designers.</p>",
            "text_font_size": "body-medium",
            "button_text": "",
