        "template--20315109818675__2c49db44-4cb6-4530-9af5-51db410b5d08-text-1": {
          "type": "text",
          "disabled": true,
          "settings": {
            "text": "<p>They'll ask, “<em>Who did the flowers?!</em>” and you'll proudly say, <em>\"We did!\"</em></p><p>Time to take the guesswork out of DIY flowers and have some fun!</p><p>We guide you through the DIY process to help you get creative, stay in-control of your budget, and have the most beautiful wedding flowers.</p>",
            "text_font_size": "body-medium",
            "padding_bottom": 16
          }
        },
        "text_AQpC8j": {
          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "text": "<p>Tell us your vision. We’ll design your plan.<br/>We build a custom flower package based on your style, colors, and budget — and show you exactly what to order and how to arrange it.<br/><strong>Get guidance.  Feel confident.  Save money.</strong></p>",
            "text_font_size": "body-medium",
            "padding_bottom": 16
          }
        }
      },
