            "heading_font_size": "heading-medium",
            "text": "<p>Tell us what you’re making, and we’ll design a custom flower package based on your colors, style, and budget — so you know exactly what to order for your wedding.<br/><br/><strong>You’ll get:</strong></p><ul><li>Easy-to-follow flower recipes for each arrangement</li><li>Exact stem counts based on your designs and budget</li><li>One-click checkout with everything you need</li><li>One free design revision included</li><li>Wholesale blooms shipped fresh to your door </li></ul>",
