    "section_double_qB39zw": {
      "type": "section-double",
      "blocks": {
        "heading_TQXJUU": {
          "type": "heading",
          "settings": {
            "title": "Why Choose Bloom Culture",
            "heading_font_size": "heading-large",
            "padding_bottom": 16,
            "heading_tag": "automatic"
          }
        },
        "heading_WDbw76": {
          "type": "heading",
          "settings": {
            "title": "Custom Designs Made for Your Wedding ",
            "heading_font_size": "heading-small",
            "padding_bottom": 8,
            "heading_tag": "automatic"
          }
        },
        "text_jA8Tpp": {
          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "text": "<p>Every recipe, flower selection, and stem count is tailored to your style, colors, and budget — so your wedding flowers feel personal, intentional, and uniquely yours. </p>",
            "text_font_size": "body-medium",
            "padding_bottom": 16
          }
        },
        "heading_n9ewqJ": {
          "type": "heading",
          "settings": {
            "title": "Save 60% on Your Wedding Florals ",
            "heading_font_size": "heading-small",
            "padding_bottom": 8,
            "heading_tag": "automatic"
          }
        },
        "text_tCGXzr": {
          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "text": "<p>With wholesale blooms and a guided DIY plan, most couples save <strong>50–70% </strong>compared to full-service florist pricing — without sacrificing style, quality, or impact. Bloom Culture customers typically spend <strong>$800–$1,800 </strong>to recreate designs that often quote at <strong>$4,000–$10,000+ </strong>with a traditional florist.<br/><em><strong>For example: </strong></em>A full-service floral quote of <strong>$8,400</strong>→ our guided DIY plan cost <strong>$1,275</strong>.</p>",
            "text_font_size": "body-medium",
            "padding_bottom": 16
          }
        },
        "heading_7NMHFL": {
          "type": "heading",
          "settings": {
            "title": "No Guessing, No Overbuying ",
            "heading_font_size": "heading-small",
            "padding_bottom": 8,
            "heading_tag": "automatic"
          }
        },
        "text_k6Amrf": {
          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "text": "<p>We calculate exactly how many stems you need for each arrangement — helping you save money and avoid the overwhelm of trying to figure it out on your own. </p>",
            "text_font_size": "body-medium",
            "padding_bottom": 16
          }
        },
        "heading_FkFmeU": {
          "type": "heading",
          "settings": {
            "title": "Experts in DIY Wedding Flowers ",
            "heading_font_size": "heading-small",
            "padding_bottom": 8,
            "heading_tag": "automatic"
          }
        },
        "text_wxMFHK": {
          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "text": "<p>You’ll work with floral designers who know how to translate professional techniques into simple, achievable steps made for real couples — not pros. </p>",
            "text_font_size": "body-medium",
            "padding_bottom": 16
          }
        },
        "heading_RAxfn9": {
          "type": "heading",
          "settings": {
            "title": "Fresh Wholesale Flowers Delivered to You ",
            "heading_font_size": "heading-small",
            "padding_bottom": 8,
            "heading_tag": "automatic"
          }
        },
        "text_Y8cePV": {
          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "text": "<p>Your flowers arrive fresh from the same wholesale farms and distributors used by professional florists — shipped directly to your door and ready to design with our care and handling guides.</p>",
            "text_font_size": "body-medium",
            "padding_bottom": 16
          }
        }
      },
